00:37:23.740 --> 00:37:25.210
The one thing I
wanted to ask you

00:37:25.210 --> 00:37:27.550
is so, as I sat here
listening to it,

00:37:27.550 --> 00:37:29.490
I was struck by how do I--

00:37:29.490 --> 00:37:33.400
I mean, besides telling
