00:37:48.430 --> 00:37:53.500
So, we've got lawyers, right?

00:37:53.500 --> 00:37:55.600
And so I've learned a
lot about copyright law,

00:37:55.600 --> 00:37:58.930
but a big part of The
Obsidian Collection platform,

00:37:58.930 --> 00:38:03.940
we're building a very
